column5: well after lots of tying and missing lots of fish i landed this nice one on saturday. trying to see a bite with rainbows on a fly is freakin hard! when you do notice you got one its to late and they spit the hook!! oh well ill be posting some nice dry fly browns once the weather gets nice and warm.
4wt had no problem landing it. and the fish just took off when it was released
Nice fish! What kind of fly were you using looks like ya have a Glo bug on there.
Nice fish,  Bet that was a hoot on a 4wt F-rod
looks like a roe bag to me bill
That is certainly a beauty. What fly did you catch that big'n on?
A long lean fish...A beauty nonetheless.  Congrats with the fly rod.
I know that place. Nice fish.
